{
  "stem": "6258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a German Luftwaffe base in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were standing there with our friends, one after another, in 16, and the SS were walking around, and shooting and yelling, and, oh, heaven.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they were making like a selection-- right, left, right, left, right, left, right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people were already going, and, to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we did not know-- as usually, you never know whether it is better to stay in ghetto, or whether it is better to go outside of ghetto into these big trucks which every day brought us to work.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So about two rows ahead of me, the others were led out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all were pushed into this courtyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was a very large courtyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were so many people that I was sure that we would be trampled to death before anything, well, happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, we were standing there, and a German came suddenly and said, now, everybody of you will go home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First, we did not realize what is going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then, everybody was so happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are not going to be transported somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then he says, but in an hour, you have to come back here with your 25 kilo of your things to take.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that-- well, he used the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It means that the very ancient city of Krakow has to be free of Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was October, perhaps 20, 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, well, she-- they start-- so they said, [GERMAN] of this courtyard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then people were really trampling one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans were shooting to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
